{"tid":2309221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西環男子高處墮下斃命　涉事大廈為中聯辦物業","createTime":"2020-12-02T11:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T12:10:28.000Z","uid":185631,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7bfb1729dcbe04b60491571fea24692844841e","tid":2309221,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"今日(2日)下午4時許，一名男子於西環英華臺8號鉑峯疑高處墮下，飛墮地面昏迷不醒，保安發現報警求助。救護人員到場經檢查後，證實已無生命迹象，當場不治。警方封鎖現場，正調查其身份及輕生原因。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料顯示，中聯辦於2015年以4.8億元向恒地主席李兆基或有關人士，購入全幢物業共48個單位，相信是用作員工宿舍或接待內地訪客，據悉，死者並非中聯辦人員，其身份有待進一步證實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201202/bkn-20201202173322543-1202_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201202%2Fbkn-20201202173322543-1202_00822_001.html&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1093a210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201202/bkn-20201202173322543-1202_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"40cbf0c8fd6ee06a0d3d1ae61a1dfe4e3a2fd79c","tid":2309221,"uid":11809,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:04:33.000Z","msg":"死人最能保守秘密"},{"pid":"1334b5987655ccc13f6dcc234a5ee88376ee49be","tid":2309221,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"支足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}